Package: actxps
Title: Create actuarial experience studies: prepare data, summarize results, and create reports
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Matt", "Heaphy", , "matt.heaphy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Experience studies are used by actuaries to explore historical
    experience across blocks of business and to inform assumption setting
    activities. This package provides tidyverse-insprired functions for 
    preparing data, creating studies, and beginning assumption development.
